snippet.title: The Salt Order | Demo Trailer (2021)
snippet.description:
Draw with salt to fight evil enemies and reclaim the stolen grimoire of an ancient order. Time for witchcrafting!

Featured on the HPS1 Demo Disc 2021 : https://hauntedps1.itch.io/demodisc2021

Get the demo for free on :
Itch.io : https://khamelot.itch.io/the-salt-order
Gamejolt : https://gamejolt.com/games/the-salt-order/513371

Animated HPS1 outro by https://twitter.com/duck_bubbles
